<hymn_number>298</hymn_number>
<title>rén shēng zài shì 迦南298</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 rén shēng zài shì zhǎi rú shǒu zhǎng hǎo xiàng yī shēng tàn xī chéng kōng.
 lái yě cōng cōng qù yě cōng cōng láo kǔ chóu fán duǎn zàn yī shēng
 dàn wǒ men yào xǐ lè yīn yǒu zhǔ bù xū kōng tā gěi wǒ men yǒng yuǎn shēng mìng.
 yǔ zhǔ tóng xíng yǔ zhǔ tóng xíng xiàng xiǎo lù xùn sù líng yáng jǐng xǐng.
 rén shēng zài shì yǔ zhǔ tóng xíng nǐ cái zhī dào hé wèi rén shēng.</lyrics>
</song>